machinevision-autoconfirmed-message: Le etiquettas accurate facilita le recerca de imagines pro tote le usatores de Commons. Dunque, per favor, face te [[mw:Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Autoconfirmed_users|autoconfirmar]], nam solmente le usatores autoconfirmate pote usar iste instrumento.
machinevision-add-custom-tag-title: Adder un etiquetta personalisate a iste imagine
machinevision-failure-message: Guai, un error ha occurrite. Reveni plus tarde o [[Project_talk:Structured_data/Computer-aided_tagging|contacta nos]].
